  - Girl
  - Mage
  dialogueLines:
  - "Let me stop you right there: if you\u2019re another \"Chosen One,\" the door\u2019s
    over there. (pause) "
  - " Actually, no. It won\u2019t let you leave anymore."
  - Great. I can make a dramatic exit without a door.
  - "So you\u2019re my new problem."
  - ' People usually call me that by our third meeting.'
  - "Saving time. I\u2019m old. "
  - Noticed. Is that mold or a beard?
  - Both. Came as a set.
  - "So\u2026 you\u2019re a mage? "
  - Was...
  - "Now I\u2019m a specialist in household-level disasters"
  - "I was told training, knowledge, power\u2026 "
  - " You want to learn? Then don\u2019t ask. Start with my mistake."
  dialogueManager: {fileID: 0}
  playOnlyOnce: 1
  destroyAfterDialogue: 1
